{"tid":1626821,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"一係唔㩒錢，一㩒就㩒盡佢！！","createTime":"2019-10-05T13:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T14:21:33.000Z","uid":295981,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"705bea38d645a820befd46cedf8f92607c730635","tid":1626821,"uid":295981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:08:11.000Z","msg":"大家重溫下個post先<br />\n咁樣做，聽日銀行就會儕提！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1620268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1620268</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於今早銀行無開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本人感到十分失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錢傍身個個緊係驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有去ATM排隊拎錢<br />\n<br />\n對於有人發起下星期全民提款<br />\n本人當然十分支持<br />\n但如果有人想呢兩日偷步<br />\n你個女個呀媽有少少溫馨提示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/faxfwtz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffaxfwtz.png&h=91345193&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W2ep9fk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW2ep9fk.png&h=750d2125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為我張匯豐卡本身已default 呢個提款限額<br />\n聽講要一日先可以生效<br />\n大家快快去set左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong>最後<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"951068c4d7619cfdd6c735ca04adf2a82198300e","tid":1626821,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:22:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad4af4a3281d657bf83f07dd42fe762c92f9a020","tid":1626821,"uid":35790,"like":